Por tani kete besim, si e fitoni?

347
00:23:00,058 --> 00:23:04,225
Problemi eshte, si te fitoni (keni) kete besim?

348
00:23:04,600 --> 00:23:06,016
Nuk ka kurs per te,

349
00:23:06,433 --> 00:23:08,225
nuk ka literature per te,

350
00:23:08,600 --> 00:23:10,849
nuk ka leksione per te.

351
00:23:11,266 --> 00:23:16,724
Por ka nje zgjim brenda jush

352
00:23:17,183 --> 00:23:21,225
qe do jua kerkoje kete

353
00:23:21,808 --> 00:23:24,266
"Kush jam Une" ky zgjim,

354
00:23:24,642 --> 00:23:27,058
"Cfare jam Une? Cfare kam arritur?"

355
00:23:27,433 --> 00:23:32,891
Kuptoni, kete do pyesni

356
00:23:34,974 --> 00:23:38,766
"Cfare eshte ajo qe kam arritur?

357
00:23:39,183 --> 00:23:42,433
Cfare kam marre prej Sahaja Yoga?"

358
00:23:42,891 --> 00:23:45,475
Do ju vijne gjithe keto pyetje.

359
00:23:45,974 --> 00:23:48,016
Por nese ju keni besim,

360
00:23:48,475 --> 00:23:50,849
jo te verber por te ndritur

361
00:23:51,308 --> 00:23:53,808
qe eshte formuar prej shume mrekullish ne jete,

362
00:23:54,183 --> 00:23:55,308
shume gjera ne jete;

363
