420
00:27:45,766 --> 00:27:49,891
Por ky shoku ishte kaq i shqetesuar, shume i shqetesuar,

421
00:27:50,308 --> 00:27:51,558
nuk mund ta kuptonte,

422
00:27:51,974 --> 00:27:53,558
"Pse me ndodhi mua

423
